      <akn:content><akn:p>Any person or health spa which makes or contracts to make any health spa sale in violation of subsection (e)(3) of this section shall be subject to a fine of not less than $1,000 and not more than the amount set forth in [§ 22-3571.01].</akn:p></akn:content>
